 / 剧情 喜剧 同性 / 上村奈帆 野村奈绪 永江二朗 Jirô Nagae / 沢村玲 田中洸希", "title": "我是家庭教师岸骑士", "type": "tv", "id": "37812763", "tags": []}, {"comment": "主人公长谷大河曾是备受期待的大学田径新星，却因成绩不佳而结束了跑步生涯。如今他在小料理店\"田实\"打工，当店主让他负责开发新菜品时，他逐渐在工作中找到了价值。另一边，为学习动画专程从韩国来日留学的研究生朴琳，终日为课题创作奔波。好不容易在截止日前提交作品，却收到宿舍解约通知要求搬离。在东京找房并非易事，琳逐渐身心俱疲。机缘巧合下，二人在\"田实\"相遇。琳品尝了大河亲手捏的饭团后深受感动，疲惫的身心都被这份温暖治愈。而大河则被琳享用美食时灿烂的笑容深深吸引。", "rating": {"count": 706, "max": 10, "star_count": 3.5, "value": 6.9}, "vendor_count": 0, "has_linewatch": false, "pic": {"large": "https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/m_ratio_poster/public/p2929168828.jpg", "normal": "https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2929168828.jpg"}, "honor_infos": [], "uri": "douban://douban.com/tv/37645091", "episodes_info": "", "photos": ["https://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2929339575.jpg", "https://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2929531215.jpg", "https://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2929531214.jpg", "https://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2929531213.jpg"], "vendor_icons": [], "interest": null, "year": "2026", "card_subtitle": "2026 / 日本 / 爱情 / 林田浩川 畑中みゆき 小山亮太 / 赤楚卫二 姜惠元", "title": "紫菜包饭和饭团～相爱的两个人相似又不一样～", "type": "tv", "id": "37645091", "tags": []}, {"comment": "本剧描述天下人丰臣秀吉之弟，武将丰臣秀长的一生；以其视角描述丰臣兄弟凭借兄弟之间的深厚羁绊完成天下统一伟业的奇迹，另外也动态地描绘战国时代的丰富多彩的娱乐事迹！", "rating": {"count": 607, "max": 10, "star_count": 4.0, "value": 8.3}, "vendor_count": 0, "has_linewatch": false, "pic": {"large": "https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/m_ratio_poster/public/p2926883580.jpg", "normal": "https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2926883580.jpg"}, "honor_infos": [], "uri": "douban://douban.com/tv/36810173", "episodes_info": "", "photos": ["https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2922250329.jpg", "https://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2927785066.jpg", "https://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2922250323.jpg", "https://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2928950447.jpg"], "vendor_icons": [], "interest": null,